name: Diário 2 - CWB Quinta de tarde (4/5)
description:
Fragment number 4 of "Diário 2 - CWB Quinta de tarde".

The fourth of 5 images that when put together, side by side, form a big panel. Think of the whole piece as an album, and each fragment as a song ;)

A visual diary that takes you on a walk with me through a city called Curitiba, in the south of Brasil. I was on summer vacation, spent most of my days smoking joints and wandering through the neighborhood. A lot goes on my mind when I see these images but I can't say it here.
